Civilians have been filmed fleeing Kiev as the air-raid sirens blast out across the city.  Traffic jams and pictures of a grid-locked city emerged on social media as residents could be seen attempting to evacuate Kiev and other cities across Ukraine. In a live broadcast streamed from his phone, President Zelensky of Ukraine urged his compatriots to stand strong against Russia and to stay calm and stay at home. Reports suggest that Ukraine are fighting back against Russia as the Ukrainian military say that they have shot down five Russian planes and one helicopter in the Luhansk region. 